        <ul>
            <li><strong>The Rails Tutorial:</strong> <%= link_to "http://ruby.railstutorial.org/" %> Rails 3.2 Basics, Asset Pipeline, Deployment, Data Modeling, Twitter Bootstrap, Behavior Driven Development, authentication</li>
            <li><strong>Rails Apps:</strong> <%= link_to "http://railsapps.github.com" %> Example applications accompanied by in-depth tutorials that go beyond Rails lessons for beginners.</li>
