            <li><strong>UT on Rails:</strong> <%= link_to "http://schneems.com/ut-rails" %> The Ruby on Rails course that Richard Schneeman teaches at University of Texas. Beginner friendly material with videos, exercises and quizes.</li>
            <li><strong>Rails for Zombies:</strong> <%= link_to "http://railsforzombies.org/" %> Learn Ruby on Rails in the browser; Go through five videos and exercises to earn zombie badges.</li>
